---
import {t} from "i18next"
import {Trans} from "astro-i18next/components"
---

<section class="lg:py-15 bg-base-200 py-6 md:py-10" id="about">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl lg:text-5xl">
                {t("about.title")}
            </h2>
            <p class="mx-6 mt-4 text-xl">
                ・{t("about.presentation")}
                <br/><br/>
                ₊˚⋆
                <Trans i18nKey="about.study">
                    Currently, I'm studying for a BSC. Computer Science at the <a
                        href="https://www.iu.org/"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="underline decoration-secondary decoration-4 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-secondary"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                >IU International University of Applied Sciences.</a
                >
                </Trans>
                <br/><br/>
                ・ {t("about.work")}
                <br/>
                <br/>
                ₊˚⋆
                <Trans i18nKey="about.lang">
                    My main programming language is <a
                        href="https://go.dev/"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="underline decoration-accent decoration-4 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-accent"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer">Golang</a
                > but I've also worked with java, python, typescript, C/C++ and more.
                </Trans>
                <br/>
                {t("about.database")}
                <br/><br/>
                ・
                <Trans i18nKey="about.opensource">
                    Furthermore, I'm a passionate open-source enthusiast and have been
                    contributing to several projects for a few years now. I've also
                    created <a
                        href="https://memnix.app"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="underline decoration-secondary decoration-4 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-secondary"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer">Memnix</a
                >, a free and open-source flashcards app for Android and Web.
                </Trans>
                <br/><br/>
                ₊˚⋆
                <Trans i18nKey="about.community">
                    I like to manage communities and I'm currently the founder of <a
                        href="/discord"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="underline decoration-accent decoration-4 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-accent"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer  prefetch">The Kafejo</a
                >, a Discord community for developers and students.
                </Trans>
                <br/>
                <Trans i18nKey="about.chess">
                    You might also meet me on a chess board as I'm playing a lot and I'm
                    managing a chess community for my friend <a
                        href="https://Stouuf.net/"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="underline decoration-secondary decoration-4 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-secondary"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer">Stouuf</a
                > on Discord, Twitch and YouTube.
                </Trans>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                ・
                <Trans i18nKey="about.linux">
                    I'm also a big fan of Linux and I've been using it since my youngest
                    age. At the moment, I'm using <a
                        href="https://www.opensuse.org/"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="underline decoration-secondary decoration-4 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-secondary"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer">Open Suse Tumbleweed</a
                > as my main operating system and <a
                        href="https://voidlinux.org/"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="underline decoration-secondary decoration-4 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-secondary"
                >Void Linux</a
                > on my laptop.
                </Trans>
                <br/><br/>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
